260
00:20:55,120 --> 00:20:56,130
Au revoir.

261
00:21:00,130 --> 00:21:01,280
Et pour Anti ?!

262
00:21:01,960 --> 00:21:03,240
Il ne vient pas avec nous.

263
00:21:03,840 --> 00:21:05,530
On a une dette envers lui.

264
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:27,240
Tsurumoto, courage !

265
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:28,390
Continue !

266
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:31,160
Sérieux ?

267
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:56,720
